name: Benditas mañanas
description:
Recently the building in front of my window's room was remodeled.
2021 is getting to the end, and also this series of lost collection gifs from 2016-2019.
I'm very happy to have the sunlight in the morning and feel the heat of this god, my plants are the happiest.
Wake and bake, a symbiotic relationship I've developed with these green fellas.
Water my plants is so relaxing.
June 6, 2019.
